query:
INSERT INTO inventory (skuId, totalStockKg, allocatedStockKg, lowStockThresholdKg, lastOrderDate, lastArrivalDate) 
SELECT id, 
  CASE 
    WHEN grade = 'ceremonial' THEN ROUND(15 + RAND() * 25, 2)
    WHEN grade = 'premium' THEN ROUND(25 + RAND() * 35, 2)
    ELSE ROUND(30 + RAND() * 40, 2)
  END as totalStockKg,
  CASE 
    WHEN grade = 'ceremonial' THEN ROUND(5 + RAND() * 10, 2)
    WHEN grade = 'premium' THEN ROUND(8 + RAND() * 15, 2)
    ELSE ROUND(10 + RAND() * 20, 2)
  END as allocatedStockKg,
  CASE 
    WHEN grade = 'ceremonial' THEN '3'
    WHEN grade = 'premium' THEN '5'
    ELSE '8'
  END as lowStockThresholdKg,
  DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL FLOOR(RAND() * 30) DAY) as lastOrderDate,
  DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL FLOOR(RAND() * 14) DAY) as lastArrivalDate
FROM matcha_skus WHERE isActive = 1;
